            "name": "Sprinkle Pixie Dust",
            "saving_throw": [
              {
                "dc": 24,
                "save_type": "Will",
                "subtype": "save_dc",
                "text": "DC 24 Will save",
                "type": "stat_block_section"
              }
            ],
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The pixie sprinkles pixie dust onto one of their arrows. If the pixie hits a creature with that arrow before the pixie's next turn, the arrow inflicts one of the following special effects instead of dealing damage. Each effect depends on the target's DC 24 Will save. On a critical hit, the target gets a result one degree worse than it rolled. \n* **Confusion** (emotion, mental) The target suffers the effects of a 4th-rank *confusion* spell.\n* **Shadow Shroud** (darkness, incapacitation) On a failed Will save, the target is enveloped in shadows. It perceives its surroundings as though bright light conditions were only dim light and dim light as though it was darkness.\n* **Supernatural Chill** (cold, shadow) The target takes 5d6 cold damage (basic Fortitude save).",
            "traits": [
              {
                "alternate_link": {
                  "alternate_type": "legacy",
                  "aonid": 104,
                  "game-obj": "Traits",
                  "type": "alternate_link"
